episodes.title: Born Into the Unbelievable: A Cult Survivor’s Story With Nachi Yavo
episodes.description:
In this episode, I sit down with the daughter of a cult—someone who was born into a world of strict control, secrecy, and manipulation. She shares her firsthand experience of life inside, the turning points that led to her escape, and how she’s rebuilding her life outside the cult’s influence. We dive into the psychological grip of cults, the challenges of breaking free, and the power of reclaiming one’s identity. This is a conversation you don’t want to miss.

This pod is sponsored by Elegant Smile.
